# Icons Directory

This directory should contain PWA icons in the following sizes:
- icon-72x72.png
- icon-96x96.png
- icon-128x128.png
- icon-144x144.png
- icon-152x152.png
- icon-192x192.png
- icon-384x384.png
- icon-512x512.png
- badge-72x72.png (for notification badge)

Generate these icons from your app logo using a tool like:
- https://realfavicongenerator.net/
- https://www.pwa-icon-generator.com/
- https://maskable.app/ (for maskable icons)

## Maskable Icons

Maskable icons ensure your icon looks good on all devices with different shapes (circle, squircle, rounded square).

Make sure your icon has safe zone padding:
- 40% of the icon area should be considered the "safe zone"
- Important content must fit within this safe zone
- Background can extend to edges
